<HL>
   The Outlook:
   Fed Seems Likely
   To Remain Cautious
   ----
   By Lindley H. Clark Jr.
</HL>
<DATE>
12/24/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE 1
</SO>
<IN>
